{"tid":2001983,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭錦滿(滿仔)當日如果唔係加入熱血公民，今日會去到咩高度？","createTime":"2020-05-05T02:44:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T06:06:21.000Z","uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5aca8cf282ef83977237f9aeac34a11e425227fe","tid":2001983,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:44:18.000Z","msg":"當年佢係拆大台第一人 知名度仲高過梁天琦 黃台仰<br />\n<br />\n加入咗熱血公民後越撈越唔掂 無論做啲咩 係啱係錯都好 都係比人笑(eg圖書館戰爭，選立會，爬渠救手足)<br />\n好多人對佢嘅印象就係食女同熱狗 而唔理佢所做嘅工作<br />\n<br />\n忽發其想 佢當年如果唔係做咗熱狗 今日會唔會有可能同天琦 之鋒等人係同一個高度呢？"},{"pid":"cfee3dab1f666620b04c2b7841501f1eeb600b30","tid":2001983,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:44:48.000Z","msg":"乞衣"},{"pid":"2785e98900c9f56b27dc5f9ba1b1f8524029e3e7","tid":2001983,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:45:36.000Z","msg":"墳頭草高度應該有米5"},{"pid":"5c8df40027ba143f79bf1b3177053d6e11aa9c10","tid":2001983,"uid":129042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:46:22.000Z","msg":"狗公"},{"pid":"ad02530eb8c3bccc242e49215b5db49069bccb47","tid":2001983,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:48:16.000Z","msg":"理性討論"},{"pid":"c6a00ba33b05cc45891d19ef443d0a5af9e94a88","tid":2001983,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:58:43.000Z","msg":"咁佢地辦一役。。。。起曬朵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真定假"},{"pid":"5ff002c34c661adf76861820f4a21261805c931f","tid":2001983,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T03:00:22.000Z","msg":"如果佢唔做政治家而走去賣大雞樂<br />\n今日大雞樂就係香港人嘅米奇老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e8e15bc9ba1864b49eb260d749d8c3ed97e09c6","tid":2001983,"uid":57797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T03:01:48.000Z","msg":"冇料冇政治智慧既人去都邊係一樣<br />\n<br />\n諗返起當年條柒頭上電視柒到出汁<img src=\"/a